title: Honeycomb: Social Parenting

creator: Honeycomb Labs
descriptionHtml:
Honeycomb makes drop-off playdates, trading after-care and taking turns with after-school activities delightfully simple to share with families in your school and community.

** Get Easy Playdates and Family Hangs **

Ditch the scheduling and endless texting! Honeycomb does the work:
- finds shared time slots through a simple approach to kids’ calendars
- prompts friends for responses, gives deadlines, manages alternate invites and sends reminders
- organizes the conversation into one delightful experience

** Share Parenting Across Families (coming soon) **

Shared parenting means kids get more social time, and parents get time back. But it’s so hard to organize! Honeycomb does the work:
- makes it easy to find opportunities through shared calendars
- manages and updates shared schedules between families
- keeps all parents up to speed on logistics with reminders, updates and changes

Honeycomb is a private community focused on pre-k through 3rd grade classroom communities.
Use Honeycomb to unlock to secret to joyful parenting: do it with friends!
descriptionShort: Find your co-parents through magically easy playdates and shared parenting.

Unlock the power of collaborative parenting through Honeycomb’s beautiful family directory, custom chat groups and magically easy playdates and family gatherings.

An easy-to-use collaboration app, Honeycomb helps parents in trusted groups –– classrooms, neighborhoods and after-school activities –– share care, collaborate on parenting logistics and just hang out. Honeycomb serves as the group's assistant by surfacing opportunities, sending suggestions, managing scheduling, and sending reminders across families –– so you don’t have to.

** Visual Family Directory **
Get to know the families, siblings and parents in your community through Honeycomb’s beautiful and private family directory. Make your child’s class or extracurricular community, or your neighborhood, come alive!

** Custom Chat Groups **
Honeycomb creates a custom chat group for your private directory, and occasionally chimes in with local family-friendly activity suggestions (weekend plans: sorted!). Create your own private groups for easy group messaging (no more contact wrangling), or direct message families.

** Get Easy Playdates and Family Hangs **
Ditch the scheduling and endless texting!
- Playdates: find free slots for playdates through a simple approach to kids’ calendars
- Family hangs: turn a chat into a gathering with a single tap
- Honeycomb does all the work: prompts friends for responses, gives deadlines and sends reminders

** Share Parenting Across Families (coming soon!) **
Shared parenting means kids get more social time, and parents get time back. But it’s so hard to organize! Honeycomb makes it easy:
- Powerful but delightful tools that make it easy coordinate share care, or collaborate on activities like summer camps or after-school activities
- Honeycomb keeps all parents up to speed on logistics with reminders, updates and changes

Honeycomb is a private community focused on pre-k through 3rd grade classroom communities.
Use Honeycomb to unlock to secret to joyful parenting: do it with friends!

title: Honeycomb: Social Parenting

creator: Honeycomb Labs
descriptionHtml:
Build a supportive parent community in weeks, not years, with Honeycomb –– the app that helps parents have each other’s backs. Honeycomb makes it easy to put faces to names at pick up, share care on no school days, coordinate after-school activities with other families, and get together IRL.

An easy-to-use, private and free chat and collaboration app purpose-built for parents, Honeycomb helps you team up with your existing school or parent community to conquer day-to-day family life, together.

And for those parents who community-build for the rest of us –– we see you Room Parents, T-Ball coaches and carpool organizers! 👏🏼 –– Honeycomb is designed to be your sidekick. Let Honeycomb nudge for responses, send event and deadline reminders, and even make suggestions for ways to share the logistics of parenting. It’s #ParentLife in your pocket.

** A Rich, Visual Family Directory **
Make your classroom or parent community come alive thanks to rich family profiles organized in a beautiful directory. Put faces to names, and be in touch with the whole family –– not just one parent. Share useful information (like your kid’s allergies and playdate sickness policy) and find families you want to connect with.

** Topic-Based Group Chat **
Put an end to noisy parent email threads and chaotic text messages packed with unknown numbers. Stay sane with easy-to-follow group chats for your private directory, all organized by topic to minimize noise and maximize parent coordination. Message your entire class, a smaller group, or individual parents.

** Shared Group Calendars **
Lighten your mental load with a shared group calendar that makes it simple to join forces on activities and summer camps, share deets and shout-out deadlines (so no one forgets teacher training day again).

** Easy Events **
Ditch the scheduling and endless texting! Seamlessly plan group events from Honeycomb chat with a few taps. Then let Honeycomb do all the work: prompting for responses, giving deadlines and sending reminders.

** Drop Off Playdates When You Need Them **
Team up to give each other a break by swapping care with a trusted parent crew. Manage snow days with care swaps, and get #datenights without the babysitter.

Honeycomb is for pre-k through elementary school classroom communities. Once your classroom is set up, Honeycomb can grow to include your kid's clubs, activities, teams and any other parent community you are part of.

The secret to joyful parenting is shared parenting. The secret to joyful parenting is Honeycomb.
